<h3><font color=green>Research</font></h3>
Design tools for embedded software (<a href="http://precise.seas.upenn.edu/">Penn's PRECISE Center</a>),
Formal modeling and verification of reactive systems,
Model checking, Hybrid systems, Software analysis,
Logic and automata theory.
